trans-unit.source: Call `Dispose` when you are finished using the <xref:System.Printing.Interop.PrintTicketConverter>.
trans-unit.target: Anropa `Dispose` när du är klar med hjälp av <xref:System.Printing.Interop.PrintTicketConverter>.</xref:System.Printing.Interop.PrintTicketConverter>

trans-unit.source: The `Dispose` method leaves the <xref:System.Printing.Interop.PrintTicketConverter> in an unusable state.
trans-unit.target: Den `Dispose` metoden lämnar kvar det <xref:System.Printing.Interop.PrintTicketConverter>oanvändbar.</xref:System.Printing.Interop.PrintTicketConverter>

trans-unit.source: After calling `Dispose`, you must release all references to the <xref:System.Printing.Interop.PrintTicketConverter> so the garbage collector can reclaim the memory that the <xref:System.Printing.Interop.PrintTicketConverter> was occupying.
trans-unit.target: Efter att `Dispose`, måste du släppa alla referenser till den <xref:System.Printing.Interop.PrintTicketConverter>så skräpinsamlingen kan frigöra minne som den <xref:System.Printing.Interop.PrintTicketConverter>var upptar.</xref:System.Printing.Interop.PrintTicketConverter> </xref:System.Printing.Interop.PrintTicketConverter>

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [Cleaning Up Unmanaged Resources](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) and [Implementing a Dispose Method](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Mer information finns i [Rensa ohanterade resurser](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) och [implementera en metod för ta bort](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > Always call `Dispose` before you release your last reference to the <xref:System.Printing.Interop.PrintTicketConverter>.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Alltid anropet `Dispose` innan du släpper senaste referens till <xref:System.Printing.Interop.PrintTicketConverter>.</xref:System.Printing.Interop.PrintTicketConverter>

trans-unit.source: Otherwise, the resources it is using will not be freed until the garbage collector calls the <xref:System.Printing.Interop.PrintTicketConverter> object's `Finalize` method.
trans-unit.target: De resurser som den använder frigörs annars inte förrän skräpinsamlingen anrop av <xref:System.Printing.Interop.PrintTicketConverter>objektets `Finalize` metod.</xref:System.Printing.Interop.PrintTicketConverter>
